

[bootstrap]
Specify N
Specify Maxtime
Every N seconds:
   suceed if (bootstrapped)
After MAXTIME seconds:
   fail


[still-bootstrapped]
Specify N
specify OkayIGuessItWorksTime  (default INFINITY)
Every N seconds:
   fail if not (bootstrapped)
After OkayIGuessItWorksTime:
   succeed


[local-web-client]
Specify socks method
Specify URI
Maybe:
   start webserver.
   wait up to TIME, checking (webserver up).

Spawn-N, check Allof (timeout T):
   Pick tor client X.
   HTTP request (over socksMethod to Tor client X) for URI Y
   Check result.


